title: Perfecly moist pumpkin bread
ingredients: ['750g pumpkin puree', '350ml vegetable oil', '800g caster sugar', '6 eggs', '600g plain flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 1/2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 1/2 teaspoons salt', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground nutmeg', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground cloves']
